574
00:42:50,234 --> 00:42:52,861
(GROWLING)

575
00:43:01,745 --> 00:43:05,541
- (SINGING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)
- (BIKE HORN HONKING)

576
00:43:05,624 --> 00:43:08,168
